data.title: Sectiunea 1-2 Exercitii
data.meta_description: SECTIUNEA 1-2 EXERCITII.xlsx - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document lists athletes who won medals at the Summer Olympics from 2000-2012, including their age, country, year of the Olympics, date of the closing ceremony, sport, and medals won. Many swimmers from various countries are among the most decorated athletes, with Michael Phelps winning the most medals of any Olympian with 23 over three Olympics. Gymnasts and swimmers dominated the list of athletes with 3 or more medals.
